OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784796493
OL,3,CGovernment to review policy after
OL,4,Cfears Pc Harper's killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,FPrime Minister Andy Burnham has said
OL,8,Fthe main perpetrator in the killing of
OL,9,Fpolice officer Andrew Harper "will not
OL,10,Fbe subject to any early release".
OL,12,FBut the new leader stopped short of
OL,13,Fguaranteeing the other two men
OL,14,Finvolved will serve their full term,
OL,15,Fbut confirmed the new Justice
OL,16,FSecretary will carry out a wider
OL,17,Freview of the policy to release
OL,18,Fprisoners early.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
