CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784796493
OL,3,CGovernment to review policy after
OL,4,Cfears Pc Harper's killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,FWhile speaking in Bath, the Prime
OL,8,FMinister was asked if it was
OL,9,Facceptable for members of his Cabinet
OL,10,Fto joke about early release after Wes
OL,11,FStreeting apologised for comments
OL,12,Fpicked up on a microphone.
OL,14,FHe said: "No, it's not, and certainly
OL,15,Fthat's been acknowledged, and
OL,16,Fapologies have been made."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
