CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784796493
OL,3,CGovernment to review policy after
OL,4,Cfears Pc Harper's killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,FReferring to the case of Pc Harper and
OL,8,Fconcerns from his family about early
OL,9,Frelease of two of his killers, he
OL,10,Fsaid: "On the broader issue, I feel
OL,11,Ffor the family, it's an appalling
OL,12,Fcrime that was committed.
OL,14,F"The main perpetrator will not be
OL,15,Fsubject to any early release.
OL,17,F"Of course, others involved have
OL,18,Fpotentially been identified.
OL,20,F"But I've spoken to the new Justice
OL,21,FSecretary.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784796493
OL,3,CGovernment to review policy after
OL,4,Cfears Pc Harper's killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,F"He will review the policy together
OL,8,Fand make further statements in due
OL,9,Fcourse."
OL,11,FPC Harper sustained fatal injuries
OL,12,Fwhile responding to a quad bike theft
OL,13,Fin Sulhamstead, Berkshire, in August
OL,14,F2019.
OL,16,FHe died after getting caught in a
OL,17,Fstrap attached to the back of a car
OL,18,Fand dragged down a country road as
OL,19,Fthree teenage suspects fled the scene
OL,20,Fof the burglary.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784796493
OL,3,CGovernment to review policy after
OL,4,Cfears Pc Harper's killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,FThe driver of the car, Henry Long,
OL,8,Freceived a 16-year sentence, and will
OL,9,Fnot be eligible for the release scheme.
OL,11,FJessie Cole and Albert Bowers, who
OL,12,Fwere passengers in the car and both 17
OL,13,Fyears old at the time, were handed 13
OL,14,Fyears in custody for manslaughter
OL,15,Fafter a trial at the Old Bailey in
OL,16,F2020.
OL,18,FBoth men might be eligible to be
OL,19,Freleased from prison halfway through
OL,20,Ftheir sentences, the Ministry of
OL,21,FJustice (MoJ) has confirmed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
