OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784796493
OL,3,CGovernment to review policy after
OL,4,Cfears Pc Harper's killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,FThames Valley Police and Crime
OL,8,FCommissioner Matthew Barber has
OL,9,Fwritten to the Prime Minister and Lord
OL,10,FChancellor, urging the Government to
OL,11,Fconsider emergency legislation to
OL,12,Fprevent the early release of two of
OL,13,Fthe men responsible Pc Harper's
OL,14,Fkilling.
OL,16,FHe said; "The killers of Andrew Harper
OL,17,Fshould remain in prison and should not
OL,18,Fbe released early.
OL,26,@xD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784796493
OL,3,CGovernment to review policy after
OL,4,Cfears Pc Harper's killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,F"The public and police officers alike
OL,8,Fwill join Andrew's family in their
OL,9,Foutrage that two of the men convicted
OL,10,Fof killing PC Andrew Harper are set to
OL,11,Fbe released early.
OL,13,F"The prospect that Albert Bowers and
OL,14,FJessie Cole could be released early
OL,15,Fwill be deeply upsetting for Andrew's
OL,16,Floved ones and will raise serious
OL,17,Fquestions about public confidence in
OL,18,Four justice system.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784796493
OL,3,CGovernment to review policy after
OL,4,Cfears Pc Harper's killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,F"This appalling case highlights the
OL,8,Fbroader problems with the Sentencing
OL,9,FAct 2026. Blanket early release
OL,10,Fmeasures for large sections of the
OL,11,Fprison population mean that many
OL,12,Fcriminals will simply never face
OL,13,Fproper punishment. This risks
OL,14,Fundermining the faith in the criminal
OL,15,Fjustice system.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784796493
OL,3,CGovernment to review policy after
OL,4,Cfears Pc Harper's killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,F"The Government must act. I urge the
OL,8,FPrime Minister to seize this
OL,9,Fopportunity for emergency legislation
OL,10,Fto ensure justice for Andrew and to
OL,11,Freduce the worst effects of the
OL,12,FSentencing Act on the rest of the
OL,13,Fcriminal justice system.
OL,15,F"The prospect of Andrew Harper's
OL,16,Fkillers being released early is deeply
OL,17,Ftroubling. The public rightly expect
OL,18,Fserious offenders to serve sentences
OL,19,Fthat reflect the gravity of their
OL,20,Fcrimes."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/9
